collection.name: Koala Intelligence Agency
collection.description:
# Recruit a koala. Save the world.

A collection of 10,000 worldly Koalas each with their unique skillsets. Their mission is to protect the world from evil.

A Koala Agent NFT grants access to an exclusive member's only club, the Koala HQ. Membership has a growing list of perks such as access to an exclusive koala-only network, IRL geocaching, challenges, and more!
